title: Birk Solutions / Spekit
content:
Analysis and implementation of solutions for a web application built in the angular framework to interact with a J2EE application with a restful api.
### Accomplishments
- Built replacement angular applications for a Java api that had front-end  components built in flash. helping to identify and test issues with the migration from an XML to JSON api (separate admin, sales and quoting angular web apps).
- Using svg library Raphael and HTML5 built a visual quote creating tool that greatly increased speed and usability.
- Built a visual tool for the uploading and manipulation of JSON-based  house plan data for use across Victoria in Porter Davis and Simonds showrooms.

title: Investorist
content:
Front end developer for Investorist.com, a business to business sales platform for off the plan property in Australia and the UK.
### Accomplishments
- Analyse user requirements and development complete development for enhancements within the asp.net MVC Web application framework.
- Implement Google maps api integration for geolocation property information visualization.
